plots: Ross and Joey are upset that Chandler told Phoebe about buying a ring to ask Monica to marry Chandler .
Ross and Joey decide to simply stop talking to Chandler .

Chandler comes to the apartment and tries to talk to the guys , but they watch a game on TV and refuse to acknowledge Chandler 's presence until Chandler stands in front of the TV and announces that Chandler 's going to ask Monica to marry Chandler , after which Joey immediately turns off the TV.

Joey , on the verge of tears and looking for tissues ( none left thanks to Paul ) announces he 's gon na cry , which is when Rachel walks in , unable to tolerate another crybaby , although she immediately becomes happy when Chandler tells her he got a ring and is going to propose to Monica .

Ross attempts to tell Phoebe the good news , but Phoebe tells Ross that Phoebe already knows and that Phoebe was with Chandler picking out the ring , upsetting Joey and Ross who go back to giving Chandler the silent treatment .
Monica 's friends talk about the engagement ring Phoebe helped pick out for Monica
